Class OfficerApplication

java.lang.Object
models.projects.Application<OfficerAppStat>
models.projects.OfficerApplication
public class OfficerApplication extends Application<OfficerAppStat>
Represents an application submitted by a user to become an officer for a BTO project. This class extends the generic Application class with OfficerAppStat as the status type.
